Description: Gorgeous Sakroots ‘Spirit Desert’ Artist Circle Large Multi-Colored Canvas Flap Backpack in Like New Condition. A fun and funky eye-catching backpack with the quality craftsmanship Sakroots (The Sak™) is known for – THIS bag will be your new favorite and is perfect for taking you from home to work, school, the gym, beach, or weekend trips in style! Features: Gorgeous high-quality cotton canvas construction in shades of off-white, olive green, brown and black with yellow, purple, blue and salmon accents, synthetic leather trim & beaded tassel accents throughout. Top cinch-style drawstring, durable brass-tone grommets and long interlocking tassels with flap-over front closure and double magnetic snaps for added security.Comfortable, flat padded shoulder straps and convenient carry handle, handle drop of 4”, strap drop of 16 ½” to 24 ½”.A roomy, open main compartment with 1 interior zip pocket and 2 slip pockets.Large front exterior magnetic snap close pocket. Side exterior magnetic snap close pockets with brass-tone hardware and beaded tassel accent.A side exterior 10 ½” zipper that opens to interior compartment with brass tone hardware, signature Sakroots round logo embossed emblem and adorable multi-color owl keychain (removable).Nice tan & gold polyester interior lining with signature Sakroots logo patch sewn in.Durable zipper, brass-tone hardware and accents throughout.Flat oval shaped bottom and brass-tone feet for base protection. Measures 15 ½” H x 13” W (14 ½” with pockets) x 8 ½” D +, 4” carry handle, backpack strap drop of 16 ½” to 24 ½”. This bag was purchased then never used and comes from a smoke / pet free home.* A portion of our sales go towards helping local non-profits in our community so thank you :)
